<CONTENT id="_3793146_1"><TITLE value="Session 6"/><TITLECOLOR value="#000000"/><DESCRIPTION
   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;h5 id="anonymous_element_23"&gt;News&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="@X@EmbeddedFile.requestUrlStub@X@bbcswebdav/xid-46884697_1" alt="" width="548" height="288" style="border: 0px solid #000000;"&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. &lt;a href="https://ia.acs.org.au/article/2024/govt-announces-new-digital-id-system-tex.html?ref=newsletter&amp;amp;deliveryName=DM23203" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Govt announces new digital ID system: TEx | Information Age | ACS&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;. &lt;a href="https://ia.acs.org.au/content/ia/article/2024/healthcare-savaged-by-cyber-criminals.html?ref=newsletter&amp;amp;deliveryName=DM20779" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Healthcare savaged by cyber criminals | Information Age | ACS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. &lt;a href="https://ia.acs.org.au/content/ia/article/2024/has-cryptoloc-solved-credential-stuffing-for-good-.html?ref=newsletter&amp;amp;deliveryName=DM20839" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Has Cryptoloc solved credential stuffing for good? | Information Age | ACS&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp; - a good news story!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h5 id="anonymous_element_24"&gt;Session Topics:&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;1. During the session we investigate the various methods and techiques employed to protect personal data and privacy&lt;ul style="list-style-type: disc;"&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;Protection from cyber threats&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;2. User authentication&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;ul style="list-style-type: disc;"&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;The known Cyber attacks identified and characterised&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="list-style-type: inherit;"&gt;How they work, what vulnerabilities are exploited.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Testing Encryption&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;For testing purposes, the following NON-HTTPS, or HTTP site can be used&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href="http://www.testingmcafeesites.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;http://www.testingmcafeesites.com/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h5 id="anonymous_element_25"&gt;Out of Session Activity:&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;h5 id="anonymous_element_26"&gt;Portfolio Tasks:&lt;/h5&gt;&lt;div&gt;Check assessments tab.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;Complete outstanding work&lt;/div&gt;</TEXT><TYPE
